20517.name: Scroll: Enchant Weapon (S-Grade)
20517.description: 10% increase in enchant success rate. . Attack power for S-grade sword, one-handed blunt, one-handed dagger, spear, and other weapons increases by 5 when enchanted. Attack power for sword, two-handed blunt, two-handed dualsword, and combat and dual-handed weapons increases by 6. Attack power for bow weapons increases by 10. Magic power for all weapons increases by 4. Attack and magic power increase two times after +4. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or sold. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Weapon Enchant Scroll - S Grade

20518.name: Scroll: Enchant Armor (S-Grade)
20518.description: 10% increase in enchant success rate. . Defence power for Grade S armor or accessory by 1 and by 3 starting from +4. It can be safely enchanted up to +3. For one-piece armor, it can be safely enchanted up to +4. Also increases HP according to level when armor is enchanted above +4. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or sold. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Armor Enchant Scroll - S Grade

Can be stored in a private warehouse. Ancient Weapon Enchant Crystal - S grade
